@startuml Chat Interaction Sequence
' Simplified Interactive Chat Mode Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend" as API
participant "Chatbot" as Chat
participant "Database" as DB

== Start Chat ==
User -> FE: Start chat mode
FE -> API: Create chat session
API -> Chat: Initialize chatbot
API -> DB: Save session
API -> FE: Chat ready
FE -> User: Show chat interface

== Conversation ==
User -> FE: Send message
FE -> API: Process message
API -> Chat: Generate response
Chat -> API: AI response
API -> DB: Save conversation
API -> FE: Chat response
FE -> User: Display response

== Generate Story ==
User -> FE: Generate story from chat
FE -> API: Extract story from conversation
API -> Chat: Get story requirements
Chat -> API: Story prompt
API -> API: Generate story
API -> FE: Generated story
FE -> User: Display story

== End Chat ==
User -> FE: End chat
FE -> API: Close session
API -> DB: Save final data
API -> FE: Session ended
FE -> User: Return to main

@enduml
